title: Supervolcano
description:
The Super Volcano documentary, capped on Discovery Channel HD. About 1hr 30min.

Documenting what would, and very well COULD happen, if we experience what is known as a Super Volcanic Eruption, at a well known Volcanic site Yellowstone Calder.

The quality is probably my best so far.. I'm not sure what I did differently, but its h.264 with AAC audio.

Thanks for your interest.  Don't expect blazing fast speed, like others have pointed out, my name may suggest. ;)
